resumes.text:
Daily Work Report 
 
Date: 16  December 2025 
Name: Aditya Chauhan. 
Project: Resume Management System 
 
 
Task 1: .Executive Summary 
Today, I focused on researching the technical architecture for an AI-powered resume 
builder and the optimal database integration using Node.js and MySQL. The research 
covered ATS (Applicant Tracking System) compatibility algorithms and high-performance 
database connectivity patterns. 
 
 
Task 2. Key Accomplishments 
A. Research: AI Resume Builder Architecture 
● ATS Optimization Strategy: Investigated how modern ATS parses resumes. Found 
that successful AI builders focus on "keyword stuffing" avoidance by using NLP 
(Natural Language Processing) to contextually match job description keywords 
(e.g., "Project Management" vs. "Managed projects"). 
 
● Parsing Technology: Researched library options for resume parsing. Identified that 
standardizing data (converting PDF/Docx to JSON) is the critical first step before 
applying generative AI.
